{
  "texts": [
    "The encoder function is to extract features from input sequences.",
    "To that end, the complete sequence is parallelly processed at once.",
    "Each token of the sequence flows through its own path inside the architecture but maintains dependencies on the paths of the other tokens.",
    "This strategy enriches each token with contextual information from the whole sentence.",
    "Encoder units (Nx) can be stacked on each other according to the task."
  ]
}